ns2:Res_Errata_Note.ns2:Text: If you’ve got any requirements relating to a disability, reduced mobility or medical condition please contact us before booking,  for direct customers online please call 01733 224 808, for all travel agents please call 0800 1073409.  We’ll be able to check the suitability of accommodation or transfers for customers travelling with a wheelchair or electric mobility aid, and pass on your requests. For any airport or airline assistance, including any medical baggage, travelling within 14 days please contact us on 0800 107 3409 or if your travel date is more than 14 days away, you can complete the special assistance form at https://www.thomascook.com/special-assistance/
Deciding where to go on holiday is a serious decision and of course it's up to you where you choose to go. Please consult FCO travel advice (travelaware.campaign.gov.uk) before making your decision.
